metadata.name: He is handicapped by a mysterious pulse
metadata.description:
White woman nod head, turn a body to come, immediately, a very beautiful in showing the appearance of cold. She does not apply powder, but the skin is white and smooth as snow jade, let a person can not help but think of "ice flesh and jade bone", "snow yan zhu lip" a few words. The facial features are exquisite and flawless, and there is a kind of sanctity and pride that makes people almost dare not look at. It is like a fairy who is stepping on the nine heaven and does not touch a trace of human fireworks.



She opened the back window, her body shook slightly, accompanied by the floating ice spirit, the whole person disappeared in the general atomization there.
